      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me paint a picture you probably recognize.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You just wrapped a 45-minute strategy call. Four people. Multiple action items. A key decision about Q3 budget allocation buried somewhere in the middle. You open your notes app. You have… fragments. A name you half-captured. A date you're not sure about. And that brilliant idea your teammate mentioned at minute 32? Gone.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been there more times than I care to admit. And the worst part isn't the lost information—it's the follow-up email chains trying to reconstruct what everyone agreed on.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.aisq.com/ktgws2gp8rd7"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then I found ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AISQ",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is AISQ?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AISQ is an AI-powered meeting assistant that handles the most tedious part of any call: capturing everything that matters. It records your meetings, generates full transcribes, creates concise summaries, and extracts action items—all automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No more frantically typing while someone's talking. No more re-listening to hour-long recordings hoping you catch what you missed. AISQ sits quietly in your calls, does its work, and delivers organized, searchable notes by the time you grab your post-meeting coffee.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-aisq"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform runs through ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "PartnerStack",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", which means onboarding is straightforward and integrates cleanly into existing workflows. Whether you're on Zoom, Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, or standard phone calls, AISQ plugs in without requiring your team to change how they already work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's the thing I appreciate most—it doesn't ask you to adopt a whole new system. It just makes your current one smarter.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How AISQ Actually Works in Practice",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's walk through a real scenario.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You have a product roadmap meeting scheduled for 2:00 PM with your engineering lead, designer, and a stakeholder from marketing. AISQ is configured to join automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what happens:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "During the call",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", AISQ records audio and generates a live transcription. You don't need to press anything. If someone shares their screen and discusses a slide deck, the context gets captured.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Immediately after the call ends",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", AISQ produces three outputs:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Full transcript",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — every speaker identified, every sentence timestamped. Searchable by keyword, speaker, or time range.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Executive summary",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — a concise overview (usually 150–300 words) hitting the key decisions, topics covered, and conclusions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
