            "text": " — automatically extracted tasks assigned to specific people with suggested deadlines.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I tested this with a particularly chaotic brainstorming session—five people, constant tangents, two people talking over each other at points. The summary AISQ produced captured the three actual decisions we made and correctly attributed action items to the right people. That's not trivial.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/aisq-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've ever tried ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "using AI tools for complex workflows",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", you know how rare it is to get accuracy that high without manual cleanup.",
