          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where AISQ genuinely shines. Instead of scanning a full transcript yourself, the AI identifies commitments, deadlines, and task owners. \"I'll have the mockups ready by Friday\" becomes a clean action item: *Design mockups → [Designer Name] → Friday.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Searchable Meeting History",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every meeting you record becomes part of a searchable archive. Need to find when someone mentioned a specific vendor? Type the name. Need to reference a decision from three weeks ago? Search by keyword or date range.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smart Summaries",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The summary feature isn't just truncation—it's genuine comprehension. AISQ identifies themes, highlights disagreements, and flags unresolved questions. You get the signal without the noise.",
